  [Text] A service brigade is to be established to absorb 
members of Umkhonto we Sizwe [Spear of the Nation; MK -- ANC 
Military Wing] and the defense forces of the former homelands 
who do not qualify for integration into the South African 
National Defense Force [SANDF]. A spokesman for the 
