<F P=101> Angola </F>
<H3> <TI>   Civilians Reported Killed in Napalm Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Civilians Reported Killed in Napalm Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB2006141294 Jamba Voz da Resistencia do Galo Negro in 
Portuguese 1200 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB2006141294 </F>
<F P=104>  Jamba Voz da Resistencia do Galo Negro </F>
<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] An MiG Sukhoi [as heard], flying from the Saurimo 
Air Force Base, today attacked the capital of Capenda Camulemba, 
dropping napalm bombs that killed 50 people, including elderly 
men and women and innocent children. An undisclosed number of 
people were wounded. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

